OL,3,CMasterchef winner closes restaurant
OL,4,Cblaming soaring costs and Covid
OL,6,FChef and MasterChef winner Simon Wood
OL,7,Fhas closed his restaurant with
OL,8,Fimmediate effect - blaming rent
OL,9,Farrears, energy increases and
OL,10,Fspiralling costs.
OL,12,FFine dining restaurant WOOD opened in
OL,13,FManchester in 2017, and the chef took
OL,14,Fto social media to say he was "very
OL,15,Fproud" of what he and his team had
OL,16,Fachieved.
OL,18,FIn a statement posted on social media,
OL,19,Fthe chef said Covid rent arrears were
OL,20,Fbeing 'demanded' by his landlord.
