OL,3,CMasterchef winner closes restaurant
OL,4,Cblaming soaring costs and Covid
OL,6,FThis coupled with issues such as
OL,7,Fenergy increases, ingredients cost and
OL,8,F'spiralling' business rates made it
OL,9,Funtenable.
OL,11,FMr Wood, wrote on social media site X:
OL,12,F"Dear Friends, Customers and Suppliers
OL,13,Fof WOOD Manchester. It is with much
OL,14,Fregret that I have to inform you that
OL,15,FI must close the doors here at WOOD
OL,16,Ffor good, with immediate effect."
