OL,3,CMasterchef winner closes restaurant
OL,4,Cblaming soaring costs and Covid
OL,6,FIn a post accompanied by a picture of
OL,7,Fthe chef, he added: "We have had 7
OL,8,Fyears as part of the Manchester City
OL,9,Fdining scene and I'm very proud of
OL,10,Fwhat the team and I have achieved.
OL,12,F"Sadly with COVID rent arrears now
OL,13,Fbeing demanded by our landlord and an
OL,14,Fincreasingly difficult marketplace,
OL,15,Fenergy increases, ingredient costs and
OL,16,Fsoon to be spiralling business rates
OL,17,Fwe just cannot make this work.
OL,19,F"I'd like to thank everyone for your
OL,20,Fsupport and patronage over the years.
OL,21,FThank you, Simon."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
