OL,3,CMasterchef winner closes restaurant
OL,4,Cblaming soaring costs and Covid
OL,6,FCustomers and supporters of Simon and
OL,7,Fhis fine dining restaurant quickly
OL,8,Fresponded to share their upset at the
OL,9,Fsudden closure.
OL,11,FOne wrote: "Genuinely very sorry to
OL,12,Fsee this news Simon. Whatever comes
OL,13,Fnext, I wish you the very best and
OL,14,Fevery success."
OL,16,FJust days before the announcement the
OL,17,Fchef shared his frustration after a
OL,18,Fnumber of diners failed to show at the
OL,19,Frestaurant.
