OL,11,Fthe caption read: "An actual image of
OL,12,Fmy chefs table at 8pm last night.
OL,14,F"I'd like to say a huge thank you to
OL,15,Fthe table of 5 that no showed, no even
OL,16,Fa phone call or a courtesy so I could
OL,17,Fresell the table."
